#trigger !eval
#name Eval Command
#type prefix
#description Evaluates the provided code and returns the result. Use with caution, as this command can execute arbitrary code.

// Eval is a dangerous command, it allows anyone to run ZBR code like Zban without being a administrator.
// Use only for IDs to only allow bot developers to use the command.
// ZonlyForIDs{ZbotOwnerID{}}
Zeval{Zmessage{}}